  "text": "Other nonpeptide CCK2R agonists have also been reported before, such as triazolobenzodiaze pinones [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The phthalocyanine agonists (SALPC and AlPcS 2 ) discovered in the present work represent a completely new class of CCK2R agonists with very long-lasting effects.",
